channel.description: Hello, I'm a new Developer. I was told by a friend of mine who owns a server that if I can find CheezScape get it up and running and show him it I can get Dev for his server. The problem is all CheezScape download links are MegaUpload which are obviously not there anymore, so I need a new link of CheezScape and I need it asap. Please help :D
